@startuml
title Management Reports - Filters, Functional Pipeline, Cache and Export
autonumber
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAF7
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #9A8700

actor "Director general" as Director
participant "React ReportsPanel" as UI
participant "Express auth + RBAC" as Security
participant ReportsController as Controller
participant AccessPolicy as Policy
participant CacheService as Cache
participant "reportMetrics.js\npure functions + lambdas" as Metrics
database PostgreSQL as DB

Director -> UI: Select financial or attendance report
Director -> UI: Set date range, branch, status, level, group/student
UI -> Security: GET /api/v1/reports/{type}?filters
Security -> Controller: authenticated director and normalized query
Controller -> Policy: visibleBranches(actor)
Policy -> DB: user_branch_access when actor is branch director
DB --> Policy: permitted branch ids
Controller -> Controller: build actor-scoped cache key\nrole + user + branches + filters + period
Controller -> Cache: get(key)

alt fresh cache hit
  Cache --> Controller: immutable cached report
  Controller --> UI: 200 + X-Memory-Cache: HIT
else cache miss
  Cache --> Controller: MISS
  Controller -> DB: non-blocking Promise.all source reads
  DB --> Controller: branches, students, sessions, attendance,\npayments, events, enrollments
  Controller -> Policy: filterList(actor, each resource)
  Policy --> Controller: branch/resource-scoped rows
  Controller -> Metrics: compose report pipeline
  Metrics -> Metrics: filter(predicate lambdas)
  Metrics -> Metrics: map(selector functions)
  Metrics -> Metrics: reduce(sum/group/average)
  Metrics -> Metrics: sort comparators + immutable projections
  Metrics --> Controller: totals, groups, alerts and chart series
  Controller -> Cache: set(key, report, 30s, report tags)
  Controller --> UI: 200 + X-Memory-Cache: MISS
end

UI --> Director: topic index -> selected subtopic only

opt export evidence
  Director -> UI: Export CSV
  UI -> UI: map visible rows and escape CSV cells
  UI --> Director: download filtered .csv
end

opt print or PDF
  Director -> UI: Imprimir / PDF
  UI -> UI: apply print stylesheet
  UI --> Director: browser print/PDF dialog
end

note over Metrics
Functional interfaces are callback contracts used by
map, filter, reduce, sort and composeMetrics.
The callbacks are lambdas/arrow functions and the
metric helpers avoid shared mutable state.
end note
@enduml
